00:26:49,170 --> 00:26:50,410
if I'd been born a boy,

541
00:26:50,430 --> 00:26:52,360
I'd have outshone all my brothers.

542
00:26:52,670 --> 00:26:54,970
My father often regrets that I
was born a girl.

543
00:26:54,970 --> 00:26:55,970
Otherwise,

544
00:26:56,180 --> 00:26:58,310
I would surely be a pillar of the state.

545
00:27:00,430 --> 00:27:01,510
So it's a case of

546
00:27:01,530 --> 00:27:03,340
talent recognizing talent.

547
00:27:03,740 --> 00:27:05,670
I've finally met a kindred spirit.

548
00:27:06,990 --> 00:27:08,390
You haven't paid yet.

549
00:27:08,410 --> 00:27:09,520
Officer!

550
00:27:09,550 --> 00:27:11,150
-You can't take it!
-Go away!

551
00:27:11,640 --> 00:27:13,030
How can this soldier bully
people like this?

552
00:27:13,030 --> 00:27:13,830
Officer!

553
00:27:13,830 --> 00:27:15,830
There are elderly at home
waiting for money to buy medicine.

554
00:27:15,830 --> 00:27:16,880
Officer!

555
00:27:16,880 --> 00:27:18,860
What's wrong with me taking
a few of your chickens?

556
00:27:18,860 --> 00:27:20,480
You just look like you need a beating.

557
00:27:20,480 --> 00:27:21,080
Get away!

558
00:27:21,610 --> 00:27:22,480
Let go! You...

559
00:27:22,750 --> 00:27:23,440
Officer!

560
00:27:24,210 --> 00:27:26,140
Your Ladyship, come down quickly!

561
00:27:31,850 --> 00:27:33,450
The Shuoxi Army has arrived.

562
00:27:50,290 --> 00:27:51,610
These soldiers

563
00:27:51,720 --> 00:27:53,240
look battle-hardened.

564
00:27:53,500 --> 00:27:55,150
Their fierce aura

565
00:27:55,170 --> 00:27:56,990
sets them apart from the
provincial troops.

566
00:27:56,990 --> 00:27:59,320
They serve under the Black
Armor Guards,
Young Marshal of Shuoxi Army.

567
00:27:59,320 --> 00:28:01,350
The Young Marshal has
fought bloodily across Shuoxi.

568
00:28:01,350 --> 00:28:02,850
His name strikes fear in enemy ranks,

569
00:28:02,850 --> 00:28:04,650
and his forces are unstoppable.

570
00:28:09,220 --> 00:28:10,030
Stop!

571
00:28:11,520 --> 00:28:12,330
Who are you?

572
00:28:12,570 --> 00:28:14,500
According to Shuoxi military law,

573
00:28:14,640 --> 00:28:16,590
anyone who oppresses the people

574
00:28:16,840 --> 00:28:18,500
shall be executed on the spot.

575
00:28:18,630 --> 00:28:20,960
Anyone caught stealing for personal gain

576
00:28:20,970 --> 00:28:22,900
shall be executed on the spot.

577
00:28:23,380 --> 00:28:24,250
Executed?

578
00:28:24,750 --> 00:28:25,790
What do your Shuoxi military laws

579
00:28:25,790 --> 00:28:27,070
have to do with us Jingzhou soldiers?

580
00:28:27,070 --> 00:28:28,640
Anyone who defies our superiors

581
00:28:28,640 --> 00:28:29,770
and disobeys orders

582
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:31,260
shall be executed!

583
00:28:31,350 --> 00:28:32,150
How dare you!

584
00:28:38,640 --> 00:28:40,840
He deserves it for bullying civilians.

585
00:28:42,370 --> 00:28:44,640
Send his body to the garrison commander,

586
00:28:44,990 --> 00:28:45,910
and tell him

587
00:28:45,930 --> 00:28:47,660
if he can't control his troops,

588
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:49,470
I, Yan Chi, will take over for him.

589
00:28:49,470 --> 00:28:50,270
Yes!

590
00:28:57,460 --> 00:28:58,260
Officer.

591
00:29:03,230 --> 00:29:04,790
Thank you, Officer.

592
00:29:04,810 --> 00:29:07,070
That's the Young Marshal of Shuoxi Army,

593
00:29:07,070 --> 00:29:08,110
my cousin,

594
00:29:08,400 --> 00:29:10,630
the legendary God of War, Yan Chi!

595
00:29:10,940 --> 00:29:12,160
He joined the army at 10,

596
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:13,990
and by 15, he was earning
top honors every year.

597
00:29:13,990 --> 00:29:15,520
Pretty impressive, right?

598
00:29:16,420 --> 00:29:17,390
Indeed.

599
00:29:18,440 --> 00:29:19,110
Thank you, Officer.

600
00:29:19,110 --> 00:29:20,240
Thank you, Officer.

601
00:29:35,480 --> 00:29:38,490
[Marquis of Anyang's Mansion]

602
00:29:45,030 --> 00:29:47,950
[Grand Princess]

603
00:29:52,460 --> 00:29:54,390
Madam.

604
00:29:54,410 --> 00:29:56,140
The Crown Prince has returned!

605
00:29:57,370 --> 00:29:58,100
Great Aunt,

606
00:29:58,770 --> 00:30:00,370
I've come to pay my respects.

607
00:30:07,770 --> 00:30:10,630
You old rascal! Still as playful
as ever at your age?

608
00:30:12,700 --> 00:30:13,510
Come here.

609
00:30:14,110 --> 00:30:17,160
The Shuoxi Army has
heavy duties at the border.

610
00:30:17,510 --> 00:30:18,710
How could your father

611
00:30:18,810 --> 00:30:21,000
possibly let you wander off?

612
00:30:21,020 --> 00:30:23,790
Guess, Great Aunt.

613
00:30:24,410 --> 00:30:26,450
You snuck out on your own,

614
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:27,140
didn't you?

615
00:30:28,430 --> 00:30:30,360
I can never hide anything from you.

616
00:30:30,640 --> 00:30:31,880
I had some disagreements with my father

617
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:33,610
over military affairs.

618
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:35,600
I ran back in a fit of anger.

619
00:30:36,170 --> 00:30:37,900
Did he strike you again?

620
00:30:40,150 --> 00:30:42,390
Why can't he ever

621
00:30:42,410 --> 00:30:44,000
grasp a father's kindness?

622
00:30:44,350 --> 00:30:45,350
I'm used to it.

623
00:30:45,570 --> 00:30:48,290
It's only because your mother
passed too soon,

624
00:30:48,400 --> 00:30:49,880
and you're his only son left

625
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:51,620
to keep him company.

626
00:30:52,030 --> 00:30:54,780
Just cut him some slack.

627
00:30:55,550 --> 00:30:56,780
He's been lonely most of his life.

628
00:30:56,780 --> 00:30:58,510
He doesn't need me to back down.

629
00:30:59,060 --> 00:31:00,060
In his heart,

630
00:31:00,880 --> 00:31:02,210
I'm probably not even half as important

631
00:31:02,210 --> 00:31:03,650
as the Shuoxi Army.

632
00:31:04,070 --> 00:31:04,940
Chi.

633
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:07,370
It's been years.

634
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:09,140
You're looking more impressive than ever.

635
00:31:09,140 --> 00:31:11,300
You were so decisive

636
00:31:11,400 --> 00:31:12,640
and commanding
in the marketplace.

637
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:13,290
Grandma.

638
00:31:13,320 --> 00:31:14,850
Gap Tooth has grown so tall.

639
00:31:15,070 --> 00:31:17,070
Let me check if your teeth are all in.

640
00:31:17,370 --> 00:31:18,600
Don't call me Gap Tooth.

641
00:31:18,600 --> 00:31:20,860
My teeth have all grown in
for a long time!

642
00:31:27,400 --> 00:31:28,050
Come.

643
00:31:41,930 --> 00:31:44,100
Chi, why are you distracted?

644
00:31:44,130 --> 00:31:45,590
Are you looking down on me?

645
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:49,370
This lady looks familiar to me.

646
00:31:50,840 --> 00:31:52,250
This is Miss Qin of the Qin family.

647
00:31:52,250 --> 00:31:53,380
How do you know her?

648
00:31:57,320 --> 00:32:00,050
I, Qin Wan, pay my respects
to the Grand Princess.

649
00:32:01,050 --> 00:32:03,810
So you're Miss Qin of the Qin family?

650
00:32:05,120 --> 00:32:05,920
Come here.

651
00:32:07,160 --> 00:32:08,420
Little Medical Fairy,

652
00:32:09,030 --> 00:32:10,480
stay away from those two.

653
00:32:10,640 --> 00:32:12,310
Don't let them hurt you.

654
00:32:13,650 --> 00:32:15,450
A few days ago on the street,

655
00:32:15,480 --> 00:32:17,000
I had a relapse of my old ailment.

656
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:19,040
Luckily, you treated me.

657
00:32:19,400 --> 00:32:20,820
Otherwise, Chi

658
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:23,490
wouldn't have been able to
see his great aunt.

659
00:32:23,780 --> 00:32:25,550
You saved someone on the street.

660
00:32:25,550 --> 00:32:26,740
Miss Qin, may I ask

661
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:28,690
where you learned your skills?

662
00:32:29,270 --> 00:32:31,330
I grew up in the Medicine King Valley;

663
00:32:31,360 --> 00:32:33,800
all the doctors and patients there
are my teachers.

664
00:32:33,800 --> 00:32:37,260
So that's why Great Aunt
calls you the "Little Medical Fairy?"

665
00:32:37,670 --> 00:32:38,470
Chi,

666
00:32:39,290 --> 00:32:40,530
how long will you stay

667
00:32:40,970 --> 00:32:42,490
in Jingzhou this time?

668
00:32:42,590 --> 00:32:43,830
Don't worry, Great Aunt.

669
00:32:43,830 --> 00:32:45,030
I definitely want to celebrate

670
00:32:45,030 --> 00:32:46,960
my cousin Jia's wedding properly.

671
00:32:47,160 --> 00:32:48,290
That's more like it.

672
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:49,820
By the way, Little Medical Fairy,

673
00:32:49,820 --> 00:32:51,380
you must come to

674
00:32:51,410 --> 00:32:53,020
my eldest grandson's wedding.

675
00:32:53,020 --> 00:32:54,420
I'll send you an invitation.

676
00:32:54,420 --> 00:32:55,950
Thank you, Grand Princess.

677
00:32:56,110 --> 00:32:56,880
However,

678
00:32:57,230 --> 00:32:58,750
it hasn't been three years
since my father's funeral.

679
00:32:58,750 --> 00:33:00,040
We're a family of generals.

680
00:33:00,040 --> 00:33:01,230
We don't fuss over such things.

681
00:33:01,230 --> 00:33:02,160
Just consider it

682
00:33:02,250 --> 00:33:03,730
as you coming to keep me
company and have a chat.

683
00:33:03,730 --> 00:33:05,640
We'll close the door

684
00:33:05,700 --> 00:33:07,360
and have our own little feast.

685
00:33:07,750 --> 00:33:09,610
Alright, I'll do as you say.

686
00:33:09,810 --> 00:33:11,980
But today, you must listen to me as well.

687
00:33:11,980 --> 00:33:13,080
It's getting late.

688
00:33:13,150 --> 00:33:15,680
I should take your pulse
and apply some acupuncture.

689
00:33:15,680 --> 00:33:16,210
Alright.

690
00:33:16,650 --> 00:33:18,780
Then I'll go out and practice with Chi.

691
00:33:19,580 --> 00:33:21,700
I still need to keep Great Aunt company.

692
00:33:21,700 --> 00:33:22,720
No distractions allowed

693
00:33:22,720 --> 00:33:24,410
during treatment.

694
00:33:24,850 --> 00:33:26,380
Did you hear that? Let's go.

695
00:33:30,070 --> 00:33:31,970
[Grace and Purity]

696
00:33:31,360 --> 00:33:32,160
My Lady!

697
00:33:32,990 --> 00:33:34,080
My Lady, look,

698
00:33:34,100 --> 00:33:35,450
I got new clothes!

699
00:33:36,440 --> 00:33:37,070
This is great.

700
00:33:37,070 --> 00:33:38,880
No more patchwork for me!

701
00:33:41,860 --> 00:33:43,970
This house is huge!

702
00:33:47,490 --> 00:33:50,100
My Lady, why aren't you happy?

703
00:33:50,480 --> 00:33:52,830
Tinglan Garden is the best
courtyard in the Qin Mansion.

704
00:33:52,830 --> 00:33:54,240
Now it's ours.

705
00:33:54,240 --> 00:33:55,600
It feels like a dream!

706
00:33:56,000 --> 00:33:57,870
These were never mine to begin with.

707
00:33:57,870 --> 00:33:59,600
What's there to be happy about?

708
00:34:02,960 --> 00:34:04,110
Wan!

709
00:34:07,030 --> 00:34:08,510
-Wan!
-Third Madam.

710
00:34:09,880 --> 00:34:11,070
Miss Qin.

711
00:34:11,350 --> 00:34:13,140
Wan, how is it?

712
00:34:13,270 --> 00:34:15,780
Is this courtyard to your liking?

713
00:34:16,700 --> 00:34:18,030
Thank you, Third Madam.

714
00:34:18,440 --> 00:34:19,300
Call me Auntie.

715
00:34:20,160 --> 00:34:20,750
Auntie.

716
00:34:24,000 --> 00:34:26,770
Look at our Wan—

717
00:34:27,570 --> 00:34:29,139
such a sweet voice,

718
00:34:29,770 --> 00:34:31,770
that face, that figure—

719
00:34:31,790 --> 00:34:33,630
truly the best in Jingzhou.

720
00:34:34,590 --> 00:34:37,679
No wonder
the Grand Princess favors you so much.

721
00:34:37,780 --> 00:34:39,330
I've been so busy

722
00:34:39,510 --> 00:34:42,219
this past year,

723
00:34:42,449 --> 00:34:45,010
so I've forgotten to bring you

724
00:34:45,040 --> 00:34:46,440
these things I prepared.

725
00:34:46,670 --> 00:34:48,670
Take a look; do you like them?

726
00:34:51,080 --> 00:34:52,320
I don't need so many.

727
00:34:52,429 --> 00:34:53,139
Keep them.

728
00:34:53,469 --> 00:34:55,270
You can alternate between them.

729
00:34:55,280 --> 00:34:57,070
When you're all dressed up tomorrow,

730
00:34:57,070 --> 00:34:59,330
it'll make the Grand Princess happy too.

731
00:35:00,389 --> 00:35:01,449
Thank you, Auntie.

732
00:35:01,800 --> 00:35:03,949
We're family; no need to be so formal.

733
00:35:03,980 --> 00:35:04,790
Alright.

734
00:35:04,810 --> 00:35:07,000
I won't disturb your studies anymore.

735
00:35:07,480 --> 00:35:08,320
Here.

736
00:35:08,320 --> 00:35:09,360
All of you, follow me.

737
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:10,800
Put all these over there.

738
00:35:11,179 --> 00:35:12,180
Put them all here.

739
00:35:12,990 --> 00:35:14,850
Yes, yes, quickly put them there.

740
00:35:17,430 --> 00:35:19,630
Such a good girl.

741
00:35:26,000 --> 00:35:27,470
[Marquis of Anyang's Mansion]

742
00:35:34,230 --> 00:35:35,760
Greetings, Your Highness.

743
00:35:40,880 --> 00:35:42,210
Greetings, Great Aunt.

744
00:35:44,130 --> 00:35:46,050
Greetings, Your Highness.

745
00:35:46,710 --> 00:35:47,880
Chi,

746
00:35:48,230 --> 00:35:49,550
what are you doing here

747
00:35:49,550 --> 00:35:51,080
instead of sitting in the front hall?

748
00:35:51,080 --> 00:35:51,750
Look,

749
00:35:52,070 --> 00:35:54,340
you're making Wan nervous.

750
00:35:54,880 --> 00:35:57,140
Miss Qin, this is our first meeting,

751
00:35:58,150 --> 00:35:58,960
but why does it

752
00:35:59,230 --> 00:36:01,030
seem like you're a bit

753
00:36:01,350 --> 00:36:01,950
wary of me?

754
00:36:05,420 --> 00:36:06,730
Your Highness, just a few days ago

755
00:36:06,730 --> 00:36:08,670
I saw you display great martial skill

756
00:36:08,670 --> 00:36:09,880
and strict discipline.

757
00:36:09,880 --> 00:36:11,480
Naturally, I hold you in awe.

758
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:14,860
The fierceness of the Shuoxi Army

759
00:36:15,050 --> 00:36:16,510
is reserved for the enemy.

760
00:36:16,880 --> 00:36:18,410
We never harm the innocent.

761
00:36:19,190 --> 00:36:21,260
Thanks to the Shuoxi Army for

762
00:36:21,720 --> 00:36:25,320
defending the nation and
bringing peace to countless families.

763
00:36:26,780 --> 00:36:28,450
Alright, alright.

764
00:36:28,520 --> 00:36:29,370
You.

765
00:36:29,400 --> 00:36:31,920
You go sit in the front courtyard, okay?

766
00:36:32,000 --> 00:36:34,070
The two of you being all
polite back and forth

767
00:36:34,070 --> 00:36:34,950
is exhausting.

768
00:36:35,300 --> 00:36:36,770
The bridal procession hasn't arrived yet.

769
00:36:36,770 --> 00:36:38,900
Let me keep you company a while longer.

770
00:36:39,480 --> 00:36:41,080
How come it's still not here?

771
00:36:41,400 --> 00:36:43,010
The auspicious time has passed, hasn't it?

772
00:36:43,010 --> 00:36:44,410
I feel uneasy.

773
00:36:44,440 --> 00:36:46,210
Go check outside again.

774
00:36:47,950 --> 00:36:50,010
Go and check.

775
00:36:52,200 --> 00:36:53,680
Yes, Great Aunt.

776
00:37:01,720 --> 00:37:02,430
Wan,

777
00:37:03,000 --> 00:37:03,600
come here.

778
00:37:05,670 --> 00:37:06,460
Sit down.

779
00:37:09,760 --> 00:37:11,230
You're such

780
00:37:11,550 --> 00:37:12,610
a straightforward

781
00:37:12,990 --> 00:37:14,260
girl,

782
00:37:14,590 --> 00:37:16,950
so why do you overthink everything?

783
00:37:17,350 --> 00:37:18,880
How did you figure that out?

784
00:37:18,950 --> 00:37:20,880
Well, I've lived for so many years.

785
00:37:20,910 --> 00:37:22,560
If I still couldn't read people,

786
00:37:22,560 --> 00:37:24,690
all those years would've been wasted.

787
00:37:25,420 --> 00:37:26,310
Actually,

788
00:37:26,340 --> 00:37:28,710
I've already found out

789
00:37:29,060 --> 00:37:30,650
all about the kind of life
you’ve been living

790
00:37:30,650 --> 00:37:32,810
in the Qin family by the time
I came looking for you.

791
00:37:32,810 --> 00:37:33,810
No wonder

792
00:37:33,830 --> 00:37:37,100
you're so cautious, afraid to
make even the slightest misstep.

793
00:37:37,100 --> 00:37:40,030
Luckily, fate brought us together.

794
00:37:40,260 --> 00:37:41,490
From now on,

795
00:37:42,270 --> 00:37:43,670
I'll try my best

796
00:37:43,690 --> 00:37:44,860
to protect you,

797
00:37:46,210 --> 00:37:47,110
so you'll never...

798
00:37:47,110 --> 00:37:47,800
Look,

799
00:37:47,820 --> 00:37:50,690
you're making yourself look
like a little old lady.

800
00:37:51,640 --> 00:37:53,210
Be happy.

801
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:54,110
Smile.

802
00:37:54,510 --> 00:37:56,040
Thank you, Grand Princess.

803
00:37:56,310 --> 00:37:57,750
Hearing your words,

804
00:37:57,780 --> 00:37:59,740
all the grievances in my heart

805
00:37:59,760 --> 00:38:01,290
have completely vanished.

806
00:38:03,020 --> 00:38:06,740
Marquis of Anyang's Mansion

807
00:38:24,220 --> 00:38:25,010
Father,

808
00:38:24,870 --> 00:38:28,020
[Yue Jia, Marquis of Anyang's Heir]

809
00:38:25,590 --> 00:38:27,180
I was sent to escort the bride

810
00:38:27,180 --> 00:38:29,040
and have safely brought her back.

811
00:38:29,680 --> 00:38:30,910
I, Wei Yanzhi,

812
00:38:30,930 --> 00:38:33,180
under orders from the Duke of Song,

813
00:38:31,680 --> 00:38:34,140
[Wei Yanzhi]

814
00:38:33,550 --> 00:38:35,000
have delivered the bride without incident.

815
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:36,480
Yanzhi, you've endured a long journey.

816
00:38:36,480 --> 00:38:37,670
Thank you for your efforts.

817
00:38:37,670 --> 00:38:38,400
Jia,

818
00:38:38,880 --> 00:38:40,210
you've worked hard too.

819
00:38:41,840 --> 00:38:44,380
The bride has arrived, and
the auspicious hour is here.

820
00:38:44,380 --> 00:38:47,700
Young Master, please kick the sedan door.

